TopicTitle: What engine is this from interstellar quest?

Articles.Content: What engine does this Dunan lander use that Scott Manley built in interstellar quest?
That looks like an older version of the low profile engine from Ven's Stock Part Revamp. Or maybe B9 Aerospace, I forget which one. I can see the atmospheric sensor model from B9 though.
They are low profile engines from b9 areospace
